{"tid":585912,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[今日(9/3)上架] A.I.C.O. Incarnation","createTime":"2018-03-09T05:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T16:22:26.000Z","uid":3873,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3448fd5455f6264fb12c56475d46b3a8e18be17e","tid":585912,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/135005_d161dec4e41a28f6297771c9ac9fde00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F135005_d161dec4e41a28f6297771c9ac9fde00.jpg&h=1d27a8bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「你&hellip;&hellip;已經不再是人類了。」世界知名影片《交響詩篇艾蕾卡 7》及《我的英雄學院》的動畫製作公司 Bones 與《翠星上的加爾岡緹亞》和《鋼之鍊金術師：嘆息之丘的聖星》的導演村田和也，攜手呈獻原創生化科幻動作影集。<br />\n<br />\n2035 年的日本，某個研究計畫發生了一場名為「大爆炸」的意外，失去控制的人工生命體「大麻煩」因而產生，佔據了整個黑部峽谷。曾被譽為人類希望的研究重鎮就此遭政府全面封鎖。兩年後，在「大爆炸」中失去家人的 15 歲少女橘愛子，從轉學生神崎雄哉得知令人難以置信的事實。她的體內隱藏著一個秘密，而一切謎題的解答就在「大爆炸」的中心地「原初點」。少年與少女相遇，人類的命運掌握在兩人手中，他們將揭曉什麼樣的嶄新真相？ Netflix 獨家，3月9日上線<br />\n<br />\n應該3-4點有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f130a13ff8c1134fc79168fc6c3df429f12a5f11","tid":585912,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:12:59.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"6490f26c2a658da662c4bfa6659c3e208b7f2dcd","tid":585912,"uid":18912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:08:12.000Z","msg":"原創<br />\n邊個寫個劇本?"},{"pid":"f172ba5aeb8878bfc5c4eeb1fb28cd7c2742f75f","tid":585912,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6490f26c2a658da662c4bfa6659c3e208b7f2dcd","tid":585912,"uid":18912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:08:12.000Z","msg":"原創<br />\n邊個寫個劇本?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:25:10.000Z","msg":"野村祐一"},{"pid":"c0a0e160193da77681d5ecbe127dbf727921e162","tid":585912,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f172ba5aeb8878bfc5c4eeb1fb28cd7c2742